  <Name>Mage Armor</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>Touch</Range>
  <Duration>8 hours</Duration>
  <Level>1</Level>
  <Description>You touch a willing creature who isn’t wearing armor, and a protective magical force surrounds it until the spell ends. The target’s base AC becomes 13 + its Dexterity modifier. The spell ends if the target dons armor or if you dismiss the spell as an action.</Description>
